Downloaded fonts from
https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto
https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto+Mono

Convert with Adafruit's fontconvert
fontconvert RobotoMono-Light.ttf 6 > RobotoMonoLight6pt7b.cpp
fontconvert Roboto-Light.ttf 7 > RobotoLight7pt7b.cpp
fontconvert Roboto-Bold.ttf 7 > RobotoBold7pt7b.cpp

Edit .cpp files
add #include "Longan/fonts.h"
remove 'PROGMEM' keywords
